data.description: Beautiful 3-2 split bedroom floor plan with all amenities! This house has it all. Fabulous kitchen with custom cabinets, granite countertops, new ss appliances that stay, main bdrm has french doors opening to the pool area, double vanity, walk in tiled shower, open living room with full masonry fireplace, recessed lighting, tankless hot water, 3 yr old HVAC, 3 yr old roof, 3 yr old siding, extra deep double garage, in ground salt water pool with robot and accessories that stay, large covered pool area with huge hot tub and grill that stays, full bath in the pool area, fully landscaped yard with drip irrigation system, sodded front yard, over sized front porch with attached carport, Simply Safe Securit system, fenced in back yard with very nice shop with power. This house has it all! A must see! USDA Elgible!
